<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-RDE_O11-B.html">RDE_O11</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The RDE/RRE is used to communicate a refill authorization request originating with the pharmacy. This message replicates the standard RDE message with a different trigger event code to indicate the specific use case of a refill authorization request.</p>
